Package com.g1.mychess.tournament.model

Class Tournament

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.tournament.model.Tournament
@Entity public class Tournament extends Object
Represents a chess tournament, containing information such as tournament details, participants, time control settings, and status. This class is mapped to the "tournaments" table in the database.
